gnu.trove.TObjectHashingStrategy, Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable, Collection, Set
public class EdgeHash
extends gnu.trove.THashSet

A set of edges, unique up to surface words. Edges with higher scores or whose signs have lower derivational complexity are kept during insertion.
